  1: # Schema.org Type Alignment - Quick Reference
  2: ## Visual Guide for Google Calendar MCP Type Mapping
  3: 
  4: ---
  5: 
  6: ## 🎯 Primary Type Alignments
  7: 
  8: ```
  9: Google Calendar MCP Types              →  Schema.org Types
 10: ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
 11: 
 12: CalendarEvent                          →  Event
 13: ├─ id                                  →  identifier
 14: ├─ summary                             →  name
 15: ├─ start {dateTime, date, timeZone}   →  startDate (ISO 8601)
 16: ├─ end {dateTime, date, timeZone}     →  endDate (ISO 8601)
 17: ├─ location                            →  location (string or Place)
 18: ├─ attendees[]                         →  attendee[] (Person[])
 19: ├─ colorId                             →  color
 20: └─ reminders[]                         →  reminder[] (custom)
 21: 
 22: CalendarEventAttendee                  →  Person + Reservation
 23: ├─ email                               →  email
 24: ├─ responseStatus                      →  reservationStatus (with Reservation)
 25: └─ optional/required                   →  (custom extension)
 26: 
 27: FreeBusyResponse                       →  Schedule
 28: ├─ timeMin                             →  startTime
 29: ├─ timeMax                             →  endTime
 30: └─ busy/free periods                   →  byDay / availabilityStarts
 31: 
 32: GmailSearchInput                       →  SearchAction
 33: ├─ query                               →  query
 34: └─ results                             →  result (SearchResultsPage)
 35: 
 36: PerformanceMetric                      →  PerformanceMetric
 37: ├─ operation                           →  name
 38: ├─ startTime                           →  timestamp
 39: └─ duration                            →  value (in ms)
 40: ```
 41: 
