349: 
350: ## Common Workflows
351: 
352: ### 1. Mark All Unread Emails as Read
353: ```
354: 1. gmail-search-messages: query="is:unread", maxResults=100
355: 2. gmail-modify-messages: action="markRead", messageIds=[... all unread ids ...]
356: ```
357: 
358: ### 2. Archive Promotional Emails
359: ```
360: 1. gmail-search-messages: query="from:marketing@company.com", maxResults=50
361: 2. gmail-modify-messages: action="archive", messageIds=[... matching ids ...]
362: ```
363: 
364: ### 3. Organize Emails with Labels
365: ```
366: 1. gmail-search-messages: query="subject:invoice AND is:unread"
367: 2. gmail-modify-messages: action="addLabel", messageIds=[...], labelId="Label_Invoices"
368: 3. gmail-modify-messages: action="markRead", messageIds=[...]
369: ```
370: 
371: ### 4. Clean Up Old Spam
372: ```
373: 1. gmail-search-messages: query="from:spam@example.com before:2026-01-01", maxResults=100
374: 2. gmail-modify-messages: action="delete", messageIds=[... old spam ids ...]
375: ```
376: 
377: ### 5. Get Account Summary
378: ```
379: gmail-get-profile
380: # Returns: email, total messages, total threads
381: ```
