632: ## Troubleshooting
633: 
634: **Issue:** "Insufficient Permission" error
635: - **Solution:** Ensure gmail.modify scope is in OAuth authentication
636: 
637: **Issue:** "Not Found" errors for message IDs
638: - **Solution:** Message IDs may have expired; get fresh list from search
639: 
640: **Issue:** labelId not found
641: - **Solution:** Verify label exists; use standard label IDs (INBOX, UNREAD, etc.) or create custom labels in Gmail first
642: 
643: **Issue:** Batch operation very slow
644: - **Solution:** Reduce batch size; Gmail API may throttle very large operations
645: 
