296: ## Date Parsing
297: 
298: The email organization system uses intelligent date parsing (`lib/date-based-filter.mjs`) to classify event emails:
299: 
300: **Supported Formats:**
301: - ISO 8601: `2026-03-25`, `2026/03/25`
302: - US format: `03/25/2026`, `3/25/2026`
303: - Text format: `March 25, 2026`, `March 25` (infers year)
304: - Weekday patterns: `@ Mon, Mar 23`, `@ Friday Mar 22`
305: - Returns `null` for unparseable dates
306: 
307: **Classification:**
308: - Past events (date < today): archive from inbox, keep label
309: - Future events (date ≥ today): label and keep in inbox
310: - Unknown: marked for manual review
311: 
312: **Implementation Notes:**
313: - Pure function: does not mutate input dates
314: - Handles missing years by inferring current or next year
315: - Used by `mark-past-events-read.mjs` to auto-archive old events
