162: **Benefits:**
163: - **Clarity:** Concurrency semantics explicit (`const limit = pLimit(5)`) vs. manual chunking
164: - **Correctness:** p-limit is battle-tested; manual chunking can have edge cases
165: - **Maintenance:** Single responsibility — library handles concurrency, we handle errors
166: - **Flexibility:** Easy to tune batch size; no loop refactoring needed
